{"tid":840350,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[國民歌手 音源女神] IU的音源在韓國如何做到獨樹一幟","createTime":"2018-09-28T15:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T07:42:16.000Z","uid":34643,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d37e0c265435b972d54cbdf0f9aae34702a6eb47","tid":840350,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"被稱為&ldquo;音源霧霾&rdquo;的IU李知恩，每次回歸都不出意料的斬獲佳績，音源、專輯銷量無短板。讓人不禁疑惑李知恩的成績是如何立足於南韓眾多solo歌手之間的？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/original/995841445AB6856937C005\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile28.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F995841445AB6856937C005&h=1c5a3eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金泰妍曾經在自己的演唱會上說過：&ldquo;感謝大家在這麼多的女solo中選擇了我。&rdquo;那麼李知恩究竟是如何正面應對臉紅的思春期等眾多音源大戶，並在其中獨樹一幟、脫穎而出呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/original/99E8D4445AB6857A074C44\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile23.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F99E8D4445AB6857A074C44&h=8fe8e0a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先是她音樂本身的國民度。國民度無關粉絲數量，而在於成千上萬的路人們的好感度。而李知恩的外貌與性格恰恰為她在國民度這一方面爭光添彩。鵝蛋形的小臉配上精致小巧的五官，不說多天姿國色，起碼是人人看了都會覺得舒服的顏值。再加上她本人親近粉絲，看上去積極而親切，任誰挑都不會有過於礙眼的地方。於是會有很多路人選擇為她的音源成績奉獻出自己的一份收聽量。其次是她本人的實力使然。不僅僅是高音低音方面的唱功了得，她對情緒的處理，對氣息的把握都會使得聽眾感到心情舒暢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile1.uf.tistory.com/original/998E4C495AB685260A7B5C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile1.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F998E4C495AB685260A7B5C&h=a233a8dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，她不僅是一位歌手，還是一位創作人。縱觀南韓，大紅大紫的愛豆大多都是創作型歌手，他們唱著自己寫的歌，發揮著自己應有的實力。李知恩也是如此，她的歌詞顯示著她的內涵她的閱歷，質量之高使任何人都無法小覷。最後，是她本人對待音樂的一種至真至誠的態度。無論是韓文歌還是中文歌，只要是她想去唱的歌她都會付出自己的時間，並讓這種付出變得顯而易見。她要做便會做到最好，做到人們只能嘖嘖稱奇而不能從中抹黑。這是她對待喜愛她的粉絲們的態度，也是對待她喜愛的音樂的態度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/original/9933FA495AB6853703EAFF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile26.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F9933FA495AB6853703EAFF&h=c973d718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於李知恩總會有不同的聲音出現，包括外貌，包括唱功，包括性格等等。有人會質疑她的高音過虛低音不穩，也會有人質疑她賣人設，實際與清純的表現不同。但是在音樂領域去看，音源成績是一個女solo實力的最好肯定。而李知恩的各種mini、正規專輯的成績在眾女solo裡一騎絕塵，也是最能代表她本人說話的東西了。其實喜歡她的人不必去在意流言蜚語。眾說紛紜，只要能聽到一首令心情愉悅的好歌曲，也就足夠了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile2.uf.tistory.com/original/99405D475AB685A61D2299\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile2.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F99405D475AB685A61D2299&h=40cbc2d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fc26b885bc18f0550e9ba2bbf393bb51ba6ece6","tid":840350,"uid":208726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d1f4745ce2749e631870135b177753b7fb3bb55","tid":840350,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc26b885bc18f0550e9ba2bbf393bb51ba6ece6","tid":840350,"uid":208726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"嘿"},{"pid":"2f612c26b7fc28e5feff11c7fceae469c5524e0d","tid":840350,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T18:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07bfc22c8ab54df75b17c0e7e8d41410fb1ae3a","tid":840350,"uid":173456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"好想做個塊朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3128cce087771814d90177dc10f8a40ddd3bd38","tid":840350,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07bfc22c8ab54df75b17c0e7e8d41410fb1ae3a","tid":840350,"uid":173456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"好想做個塊朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T18:57:25.000Z","msg":"你看起來很好吃！"},{"pid":"da46d868bcc7f277d90a7ea1114741effc1c825a","tid":840350,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53972597d2fa5bf323f3a43f1e65138322156c5","tid":840350,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07bfc22c8ab54df75b17c0e7e8d41410fb1ae3a","tid":840350,"uid":173456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"好想做個塊朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"好想比iu咬春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d2e09d13e4d68bd81f53896d6de3ef0866e854","tid":840350,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"可惜仲未超越太妍"},{"pid":"6b9bc8c8a82f3c4f502a1fd7972a0899f8ac70fa","tid":840350,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da46d868bcc7f277d90a7ea1114741effc1c825a","tid":840350,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}